ize: x-large;\"><strong>袁志偉令公司蝕錢 諗起都笑出聲</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1298384/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1298384/page/1</a><br />\n狙擊日日玩抹黑既CCTVB<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>五大訴求達成前 絕不對話</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1298529/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1298529/page/1</a><br />\n777想搞傘運對話2.0 ，邊個去就拉邊個！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><br />\n［突發］林鄭將於9:30am會見傳媒</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1298339/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1298339/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n777對刁民態度軟弱 無能力管治香港！<br />\n點解死都唔講撤回　即是有古怪！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">幫推唔該，而家劣勢緊！！！<br />\n做好文宣準備來日動向！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"918e79b98923b725e2119acd30aaf454d26a6b64","tid":1298653,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:21:58.000Z","msg":"香港人　加油！"},{"pid":"f763c0f5de4de6e51c3149a5117d525acd602119","tid":1298653,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:22:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de9f929fb9724d6a4dcae1b160d734bd8bef82ba","tid":1298653,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:23:07.000Z","msg":"義士未救，血債未償！<br />\n今次輸，以後就是警察世界！"},{"pid":"91cf71e8600d6720559b3230cd744c092f102035","tid":1298653,"uid":190101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:23:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42aab357a64ab4e4dc462af0024af3a0dffbf012","tid":1298653,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:25:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"675b9933ecf15262505455cc850bbfda6f81aedf","tid":1298653,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:25:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59a5f7ad7920028825